        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/16653317/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/16653317/" class="">第391页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/guthrun/" class=" " title="Ag | Bd">Ag | Bd</a>
                (We are Infinite.)
              
                <span class="allstar50" title="力荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="16653317">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">文凭是为了混饭，跟艺术有什么关系？单位用人要文凭，因为单位的第一要义是平庸。文凭是平庸的保证。他们绝对不会要凡·高。</span>
                  &nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/16653317/">(<span class="">1回应</span>)</a>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2012-02-09 18:38</span>
                  
                    &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="">6人喜欢</span>
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <blockquote><q>文凭是为了混饭，跟艺术有什么关系？单位用人要文凭，因为单位的第一要义是平庸。文凭是平庸的保证。他们绝对不会要凡·高。</q></blockquote>
